name: Neural Iterations 0041
description:
Diversification of thought allows for different ideas to come to fruition. Mazes allow for a resemblance of neural pathways and a kernel ‘idea’. Generative evolutionary optimization of the neural pathways allows divergence to be explored and visualized, the ‘idea’ still within. 

The series features the optimized neural pathways of 2800 evolutionary iterations.
